        <li><strong>AICTE Scholarships:</strong> The All India Council for Technical Education provides scholarships for deserving students.</li>
        <li><strong>State Government Scholarships:</strong> Each state government offers scholarships for students domiciled in their respective states.</li>
        <li><strong>Private and University-Specific Scholarships:</strong> Many private organizations and universities offer scholarships to architecture students.</li>
